<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1302 gunēṁṭi bhādravada śuddhāṣṭami gu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ruvāramunāṁḍu pātraśrīrāmujīyana śiṣṭu sōmāyibhāra
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ki tanaku Iṣṭarththasiddhigā śrīnarasiṁhmanāthuni śrībhaṁḍāra
<lb n="4" break="no"/>maṁdu padmanidhimāḍalu 9 nni peṭṭi prasādamu kuṁcalu 2 vṛ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ttigāṁ paḍasi śrīnārasiṁhanāthuniki nityamunnu māpaṭi
<lb n="6"/>dhūpaAvasaramaṁdu tirumālalu reṁḍu 2 catiṁpasa Aḷa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gunāyuṁḍu Adhiṣṭatagānu bhūmi Annama tecipeṭi Ī prasāda
<lb n="8" break="no"/>mu reṁḍu kuṁccalunnū bhujiṁpaṁgalāṁḍu Īmaḷalu reṁṭikinni
<lb n="9"/>nibaṁdha samasya jītāmu Apamu viḍiyamu cellaṁgaldu
<lb n="10"/>[Ī dharmmu] śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

